== Documentation ==
This template is used to tag additions as upcoming to text inline. It will also add an Upcoming category.

<nowiki>{{1}}</nowiki> is the text that will be displayed

<nowiki>{{2}}</nowiki>  is the link that will be used for the text. It appends <code>https://</code> automatically.

=== Example Usage ===
* <code><nowiki>{{Upcoming_inline}}</nowiki></code> will make: {{Upcoming_inline|nocat=1}}
* <code><nowiki>{{Upcoming_inline|2025.3.2}}</nowiki></code> will make: {{Upcoming_inline|2025.3.2|nocat=1}}
* <code><nowiki>{{Upcoming_inline|2025.3.2|docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202532}}</nowiki></code> will make: {{Upcoming_inline|2025.3.2|docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202532|nocat=1}}

